citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1154 on
29-Aug-17.
Inspector arrival to facility at 1154 No answer at door, called home # and left message. Called cell # and spoke
with owner. Owner stated they were currently out of town and no individual available for facility inspection at this
time.
